title: Tim Holtz - Ranger EMBOSSING PEN 2PK
description: These pens contain a specially formulated clear ink that works with Distress Embossing Glaze (sold separately). The ink stays wet on most surfaces to allow working time to create your own designs. This 3x7.75x.5 inch package contains one bullet tip pen and one brush tip pen. Non-toxic. Acid free. Conforms to ASTM D 4236. Made in USA.
